# TopOpt Studio — remote run target (optional, personal config).
# Copy to web/.env.local (gitignored) and adjust. When VITE_REMOTE_HOST is set,
# the Run panel shows a "Distant" target: a machine that has cloned + built
# this repo and runs `node server/run-server.mjs --host 0.0.0.0` (e.g. a Mac
# Studio reachable over Tailscale — the IP below is just an example).
#
# VITE_REMOTE_HOST=100.82.100.44
# VITE_REMOTE_PORT=8787
